Recent multiple posts can be avoided as follows:
 
 When you get the "There appears to be a problem with the Website server..." (or something similar on your browser)...the tendency is to tag "Submit post" again.
 
 If you will tag "Back" a couple of times, get back to the home page, find the thread again, you will see that your post was recorded in the thread.
